{"word":"G3471 - μωραίνω - mōraínō - mo-rah'-ee-no - Become fool","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μωραίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mōraínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mo-rah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Become fool</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சாரமற்றுப்போ, பைத்தியமாகு"},{"paragraph":"1. to be foolish, to act foolishly"},{"paragraph":"2. to make foolish, to make flat and tasteless"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3474 - μωρός - mōrós - mo-ros'/3474\">G3474</a>; to <i>become insipid</i>; figuratively to <i>make</i> (passively <i>act</i>) as a <i>simpleton:</i> - become fool, make foolish, lose savour.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3471/3471\">G3471</a>, <a href=\"#/G3472/3472\">G3472</a>, <a href=\"#/G3473/3473\">G3473</a>, <a href=\"#/G3474/3474\">G3474</a>"}]}